{"type":"message","id":"a51e6f7b","parentId":"6e6f1431","timestamp":"2026-04-25T10:41:30.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"又推进了一步，这次不是 key 了。\n\n现在的真实报错是：\n- `503`\n- `model gpt-image-2 is only supported on /v1/images/generations and /v1/images/edits`\n\n结论很明确：\n- 你现在这组 key 已经可用了\n- 但当前 `gpt-image-generator` 这个脚本走的是 `/v1/responses`\n- 而你这个服务端的 `gpt-image-2` 只接受 `/v1/images/edits` 或 `/v1/images/generations`\n- 所以现在卡的是接口路由不兼容，不是图片、不是真人脸、不再是密钥问题\n\n你现在最合适的下一步有两个：\n\n1. 我直接帮你改这个 skill / 脚本，让它走 `/v1/images/edits`，然后继续出图  \n2. 你那边如果已经有现成支持 `/v1/images/edits` 的脚本或接口，我帮你把最终修图提示词整理成可直接调用版本\n\n我建议选 1，我可以直接接着改。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ec9a55ba70819790e881f58f133677\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":37171,"output":249,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37420,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777113683799,"responseId":"resp_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ec9a54c7f881979f34287399678c90"}}
