{"type":"message","id":"ae85299e","parentId":"7464d552","timestamp":"2026-04-25T10:50:15.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"记住了。\n\n以后你让我修双人照，尤其是登记照、证件照这类，我会默认遵守这条：\n- 不改男生和女生脸型\n- 不改原本面部表情\n- 优先保真五官、神态和相似度\n\n如果你要，我现在也可以按这条更严格的要求，把刚才那张再重修一版。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ec9c651c6881978fb9b651586bdd6c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":49281,"output":94,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49375,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777114209895,"responseId":"resp_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ec9c6332d481978566db4f164d3516"}}
