{"type":"message","id":"ef8b5cd9","parentId":"d0d6fdd4","timestamp":"2026-04-25T11:04:38.521Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/14dce90d-da7a-4406-9c70-3dbf3fb96b3d.jpg (image/*)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths - they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1777115074912-7e9dc567\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 19:04 GMT+8\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1777115078434}}
{"type":"message","id":"b6752952","parentId":"ef8b5cd9","timestamp":"2026-04-25T11:04:52.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到，我直接按新图重做。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ec9fcb7b8c8197bacbf5db74248a71\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_oZmgo8rq3CCMeyRvRytGtNHI|fc_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ec9fcbe5908197a528b16edee18e49","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/tmp/run_wedding_edit_newphoto.sh","content":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL='http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses'\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY='[REDACTED]'\npython3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py \\\n  --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/14dce90d-da7a-4406-9c70-3dbf3fb96b3d.jpg \\\n  --prompt '将这张双人原图重新制作成自然真实的中国结婚登记照，核心目标是自然、像本人、不过度修饰。必须严格保持两位人物原始脸型、五官比例、面部结构、眼型、鼻型、嘴型和原本的面部表情，不要换脸，不要改表情，不要瘦脸，不要放大眼睛，不要重塑鼻梁，不要改变牙齿，不要做明显磨皮，不要做网红脸。只做结婚登记照所需的必要调整：统一为两寸证件照风格，3:2比例，半身构图，从胸部上方到头顶，保留适当头顶空间；构图为女左男右，女性在前，男性略侧后但贴近，姿态自然；背景改为纯色深红色#8B0000，无渐变；光线整理为正面柔和均匀布光，无明显阴影；服装替换为正式登记照风格，女性穿简洁纯白色礼服裙，男性穿深色正式西装白衬衫领带。整体效果要像真实影楼拍摄的结婚登记照，审美克制、自然、正式、真实，最优先保证人物像原图本人。' \\\n  --out-base wedding-registration-photo-new\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/tmp/run_wedding_edit_newphoto.sh\",\"content\":\"#!/usr/bin/env bash\\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL='http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses'\\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY='[REDACTED]'\\npython3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py \\\\\\n  --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/14dce90d-da7a-4406-9c70-3dbf3fb96b3d.jpg \\\\\\n  --prompt '将这张双人原图重新制作成自然真实的中国结婚登记照，核心目标是自然、像本人、不过度修饰。必须严格保持两位人物原始脸型、五官比例、面部结构、眼型、鼻型、嘴型和原本的面部表情，不要换脸，不要改表情，不要瘦脸，不要放大眼睛，不要重塑鼻梁，不要改变牙齿，不要做明显磨皮，不要做网红脸。只做结婚登记照所需的必要调整：统一为两寸证件照风格，3:2比例，半身构图，从胸部上方到头顶，保留适当头顶空间；构图为女左男右，女性在前，男性略侧后但贴近，姿态自然；背景改为纯色深红色#8B0000，无渐变；光线整理为正面柔和均匀布光，无明显阴影；服装替换为正式登记照风格，女性穿简洁纯白色礼服裙，男性穿深色正式西装白衬衫领带。整体效果要像真实影楼拍摄的结婚登记照，审美克制、自然、正式、真实，最优先保证人物像原图本人。' \\\\\\n  --out-base wedding-registration-photo-new\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":54340,"output":503,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54843,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777115078521,"responseId":"resp_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ec9fc8a7148197b6feaeefaf9872d6"}}
