{"type":"message","id":"31452346","parentId":"f97abcec","timestamp":"2026-04-25T15:17:24.947Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/a0dea35f-61fb-472e-8294-ec843e571e62.jpg (image/*)]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths - they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1777130241557-fc00ca8d\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 23:17 GMT+8\"\n}\n```"}],"timestamp":1777130244876}}
{"type":"message","id":"c70ccdaf","parentId":"31452346","timestamp":"2026-04-25T15:17:40.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到新原图，我直接按你那套登记照规格重生一张。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ecdb09bf748197995e9794cceeab63\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_JeAs0VE2apCAEF8TacK31CjN|fc_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ecdb0a54108197ace05c2cc6ac782a","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/tmp/run_wedding_edit_latest.sh","content":"#!/usr/bin/env bash\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL='http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses'\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY='[REDACTED]'\npython3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py \\\n  --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/a0dea35f-61fb-472e-8294-ec843e571e62.jpg \\\n  --prompt '根据这张原图重新生成一张中国结婚登记照。必须严格保持原图人物五官、脸型和原本面部表情，不换脸，不改神态，人物要像本人。成片为两寸证件照风格，3:2比例，半身照，从胸部上方到头顶，保留适当头顶空间。构图为女左男右，女性在前，男性略侧后，但两方外侧肩膀基本齐平，女性两侧肩膀齐平，男性肩膀在女性肩膀后侧略贴紧，女性正脸朝前，男性头部稍微朝中间，平视正面拍摄。背景改为纯色深红色背景，颜色#8B0000，无渐变，色彩饱满均匀。光线为正面柔和打光，无明显阴影，光线均匀。女性保留黑色长发过胸，轻度蓬松，头发整洁，露出额头、眉毛和双耳，一侧长发在前，穿纯白色法式轻奢缎面无袖礼服裙，姿态端庄优雅。男性保留自然真实状态，穿蓝黑色双排扣西装、纯白色标准领衬衫、蓝黑色带金色或浅色小圆点图案领带，站姿挺拔。整体风格正式、优雅、温馨，氛围庄重而不失亲切，像真实影楼拍摄的经典结婚登记照，自然真实，不夸张修饰。' \\\n  --out-base wedding-registration-photo-latest\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/tmp/run_wedding_edit_latest.sh\",\"content\":\"#!/usr/bin/env bash\\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL='http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses'\\nexport PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY='[REDACTED]'\\npython3 /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py \\\\\\n  --image /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/media/inbound/a0dea35f-61fb-472e-8294-ec843e571e62.jpg \\\\\\n  --prompt '根据这张原图重新生成一张中国结婚登记照。必须严格保持原图人物五官、脸型和原本面部表情，不换脸，不改神态，人物要像本人。成片为两寸证件照风格，3:2比例，半身照，从胸部上方到头顶，保留适当头顶空间。构图为女左男右，女性在前，男性略侧后，但两方外侧肩膀基本齐平，女性两侧肩膀齐平，男性肩膀在女性肩膀后侧略贴紧，女性正脸朝前，男性头部稍微朝中间，平视正面拍摄。背景改为纯色深红色背景，颜色#8B0000，无渐变，色彩饱满均匀。光线为正面柔和打光，无明显阴影，光线均匀。女性保留黑色长发过胸，轻度蓬松，头发整洁，露出额头、眉毛和双耳，一侧长发在前，穿纯白色法式轻奢缎面无袖礼服裙，姿态端庄优雅。男性保留自然真实状态，穿蓝黑色双排扣西装、纯白色标准领衬衫、蓝黑色带金色或浅色小圆点图案领带，站姿挺拔。整体风格正式、优雅、温馨，氛围庄重而不失亲切，像真实影楼拍摄的经典结婚登记照，自然真实，不夸张修饰。' \\\\\\n  --out-base wedding-registration-photo-latest\\n\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":65692,"output":576,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66268,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777130244947,"responseId":"resp_0915ba638edbc8bc0169ecdb07c4cc8197a7bfa16e7555d91d"}}
